Area Forecast Discussion
National Weather Service San Francisco CA
454 AM PDT Sun Mar 10 2024

...New AVIATION, MARINE...

.SYNOPSIS...
Issued at 1259 AM PST Sun Mar 10 2024

Two weak systems will bring light rain to the region during the
day today as well as late Monday into Tuesday. As conditions dry
out, breezy northerly winds will develop midweek. Winds diminish
by the end of the week and temperatures will continue to rise to
seasonably warm temperatures under influence of strong high
pressure.

